categories: Category:Imperial Navy personnel of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: A technician served under a unidentified officer in the blockade above Lothal. When Chopper, disguised as droid 264, arrived on the light cruiser Tellstar, he told him he was late and told him to plug in. However, the data did not come in, and the technician told his officer that the droid was malfunctioning.
